{"tid":2212281,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"胡孟青：匯豐兩邊不是人  視乎感情多厚沽出","createTime":"2020-09-21T16:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T16:38:59.000Z","uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"471203f00d741f4ffdb5bd26bd4ce3bcaf1a591c","tid":2212281,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:14:44.000Z","msg":"匯豐股價未見底，匯豐股價在倫敦時段進一步失守29元，迫近28元的世紀供股價。曾經因為匯豐股價急跌而落淚的獨立股評人胡孟青，接受《香港經濟日報》訪問時表示，環球息口未來3年難上升，不僅匯豐受影響，其他銀行也受壓，投資者應擔心環球銀行股前景，不排除未來銀行界會有更多合併或重組，預期匯豐股價會持續尋底。<br />\n<br />\n胡孟青指，匯豐股價周一（21日）加速沉底，明顯與市場擔心匯豐會被列入《不可靠實體清單》有關。她認為，若本身沒有匯豐股票，現階段不急於「撈底」，若持有滙豐多年，收息已覆蓋了投資成本，<strong>是否沽出匯豐，就要視乎你對匯豐的感情有多厚</strong>，若有其他需要，不妨換馬。"},{"pid":"57e5f30e34377ca6bc69fa16b0caa0461c0d25c6","tid":2212281,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:16:28.000Z","msg":"有錢有感情<br />\n冇錢冇感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462f21458d778a57910da5b12b5b05ad879d0b85","tid":2212281,"uid":62850,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:18:34.000Z","msg":"炒股講感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21805b1b9351afacb593ac3d98d2ee37fa1fed6a","tid":2212281,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:35:00.000Z","msg":"感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />傻撚咗定昆人？怪得知買股票買都流馬尿"},{"pid":"9156d4dce3b5ce08abc54fcfab2165975061f8b4","tid":2212281,"uid":139173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:38:59.000Z","msg":"睇完成段嘢都唔知佢噏乜春<br />\n不如即場表演青姐淚算啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}